 title=\"Skyrim:Frost Giant\">Frost Giant</a><sup><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dawnguard\" title=\"Skyrim:Dawnguard\">DG</a></sup></td>\n<td>Grand\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Frost_Troll\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Frost Troll\">Frost Troll</a></td>\n<td>Common\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Frostbite_Spider\" title=\"Skyrim:Frostbite Spider\">Frostbite Spider</a></td>\n<td>Petty\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Lesser\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Gargoyle\" title=\"Skyrim:Gargoyle\">Gargoyle</a><sup><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dawnguard\" title=\"Skyrim:Dawnguard\">DG</a></sup></td>\n<td>Lesser\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Giant_Frostbite_Spider\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Giant Frostbite Spider\">Giant Frostbite Spider</a></td>\n<td>Lesser\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Giant\" title=\"Skyrim:Giant\">Giant</a></td>\n<td>Greater\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Goat\" title=\"Skyrim:Goat\">Goat</a></td>\n<td>Petty\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Hagraven\" title=\"Skyrim:Hagraven\">Hagraven</a></td>\n<td>Common\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Horker\" title=\"Skyrim:Horker\">Horker</a></td>\n<td>Petty\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Horse\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Horse\">Horse</a></td>\n<td>Lesser\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Hulking_Draugr\" title=\"Skyrim:Hulking Draugr\">Hulking Draugr</a><sup><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dawnguard\" title=\"Skyrim:Dawnguard\">DG</a></sup></td>\n<td>Common\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Ice_Wolf\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Ice Wolf\">Ice Wolf</a></td>\n<td>Lesser\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Ice_Wraith\" title=\"Skyrim:Ice Wraith\">Ice Wraith</a></td>\n<td>Lesser\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:King_Olaf_One-Eye\" title=\"Skyrim:King Olaf One-Eye\">King Olaf One-Eye</a></td>\n<td>Commo